  <brief_title>Pressure and Temperature Sensor for Therapeutic Compression Garments</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-label Preliminary Assessment of a Thin Flexible Pressure and Temperature Sensor for Therapeutic Compression Garments Using a Cohort of Healthy Adults</official_title>
