  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pilot study of a soft, flexible pressure and temperature sensor
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of safety, and preliminary accuracy of a pressure and temperature sensor adherent
      to the skin. The pressure sensor includes a piezoresistive fabric coupled to a near-field
      communication chip with a built-in temperature sensor.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
